364/dan-alta-primer-paciente-valenciano-coronavirus.html |title=Dan de alta el primer paciente valenciano diagnosticado con coronavirus |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[La Vanguardia]] |publisher=La Vanguardia Ediciones, S.L.U. |language=es}}</ref><ref name=\"auto11\">{{cite news |url=https://www.europapress.es/comunitat-valenciana/noticia-nuevo-caso-coronoavirus-alicante-alta-castellon-dejan-numero-contagiados-comunitat-30-20200306185059.html |title=Un nuevo caso de coronavirus en Alicante deja el n\u00famero de contagios en la Comunitat Valenciana en 31 |date=6 March 2020 |access-date=6 March 2020 |newspaper=[[Europa Press]] |publisher=Europa Press Noticias S.A. |language=es}}</ref>\n* The [[Episcopal Conference of Spain|Spanish Episcopal Conference]] indicated that churches should remove the holy water from the pillars, avoid the gesture of shaking hands as a way of giving peace, and not kiss religious images, a typical gesture in [[Lent]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://conferenciaepiscopal.es/indicaciones-de-la-cee-ante-el-coronavirus/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=indicaciones-de-la-cee-ante-el-coronavirus|title=Indicaciones de la CEE ante el coronavirus|website=conferenciaepiscopal.es|access-date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n; 7 March\n* A student of Colegio Santa Mar\u00eda de los Rosales in [[Madrid]] tested positive for the coronavirus. This is the college where [[Leonor, Princess of Asturias]], [[heir presumptive]] to the throne of [[Spain]] and her sister [[Infanta Sof\u00eda of Spain|Infanta Sof\u00eda]] study. The [[Royal Household of Spain]] announced that the daughters of the King would attend classes when they resume on Monday.<ref>{{cite news |title=Un estudiante del colegio de la Princesa Leonor, contagiado de coronavirus|url=https://www.larazon.es/gente/20200307/tj3fa2ftrvf4haeqzfps3nyk3u.html|date=7 March 2020 |access-date=7 March 2020 |newspaper=[[La Raz\u00f3n (Madrid)|La Raz\u00f3n]] |publisher=Europa Press Notic