lemadrid.es/noticias/madrid/Madrid-retrasa-semanas-calendario-academico-0-2211978814--20200310103154.html|title=Madrid retrasa dos semanas el calendario acad\u00e9mico|website=telemadrid.es|date=10 March 2020|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Spanish Government suspends events with more than one thousand attendants in Madrid, La Rioja and Vitoria.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eldiario.es/sociedad/Sanidad-consejo-ministros-medidas_0_1004400105.html|title=El Gobierno suspende los eventos a cubierto de m\u00e1s de mil personas en Madrid, La Rioja y Vitoria|last=Remacha|first=Bel\u00e9n|website=eldiario.es|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* The [[Generalitat Valenciana|Valencian Government]] decides to postpone the [[Falles|Falles of Valencia]] for the fifth time in its history and the [[Magdalena Festival|Magdalena]], in Castell\u00f3n.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eldiario.es/cv/Gobierno-prohibe-multitudinarios-Fallas-coronavirus_0_1004400103.html|title=El Gobierno valenciano aplaza las Fallas de Val\u00e8ncia y la Magdalena de Castell\u00f3n por el coronavirus|website=eldiario.es|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n;11 March\n* The Catalan government followed the steps of the Spanish government taken the previous day and suspended events with more than one thousand attendees in the region.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eldiario.es/catalunya/Catalunya-prohibe-eventos-personas-coronavirus_0_1004749678.html|title=Catalunya proh\u00edbe los eventos de m\u00e1s de 1.000 personas por la crisis del coronavirus|last=Rodr\u00edguez|first=Pau|website=eldiario.es|language=es|access-date=11 March 2020}}</ref>\n* Madrid cancelled the main tribute in honour of the [[2004 Madrid train bombings|11-M terrorist attacks]] in Atocha.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ultimahora.es/noticias/nacional/2020/03/11/1147631/madrid-coronavirus-condiciona-aniversario-del-11m.html|title=Un 11M m\u00e1s, pero no uno cualquiera|date=11 March 2020|website=